import { Box } from "@mui/material"
const Summation = ({ breakfast, lunch, dinner, snacks }) => {
  return (

    <>
    <Box sx={{width:'100%',display:'flex',alignItems:'right'}}>
      <Box sx={{ width: '100%', textAlign: 'center', }}>{breakfast.reduce((total, food) => (total + food.cal), 0) + ' cal'}</Box>
    </Box>

      <Box sx={{ width: '100%' }}>{lunch.reduce((total, food) => (total + food.cal), 0)}</Box>

      <Box sx={{ width: '100%' }}>{dinner.reduce((total, food) => (total + food.cal), 0)}</Box>

      <Box sx={{ width: '100%' }}>{snacks.reduce((total, food) => (total + food.cal), 0)}</Box>
    </>
  )
}

export default Summation
